home.row1-1: Ability Arena is an autobattler that mixes the fun of games such as Auto Chess, Atomic War, and Underlords with the depth and variety of Ability Draft.
home.row2-2: Mix and match Spells to create cool combos
home.row2-3: No economy - Your gold will reset every round
home.row2-5: 150 spells in the game, with 50 of those being banned randomly each game
home.row2-6: Each spell has 20 copies in the game, which are in a shared pool with the other players
home.row8-2: Buy duplicate spells to increase their spell points
home.row8-3: 3 points = Standard Level spell (equivalent to a max level spell in Dota
home.row8-4: 6 points = Super Level spell (gives a power talent, shard or item)
home.row8-5: 9 points = Gaben Level spell (give something crazy)
home.row8-6: Heroes will try to cast spells from left to right
home.row3-2: Pick from a variety of Gods, each with their own unique abilities and synergies
home.row3-3: Unlock new Gods by opening God Chests, as well as through the Battle Pass each month
home.row3-4: Gods come from various Valve universes. Who will be next?
home.row4-2: Hero bodies are given periodically through the game
home.row4-3: Bodies are separated into tiers based on their power (S, A, B, C, D)
home.row4-5: Includes your regular Dota cosmetics for free
home.row4-6: Hero levels are equivalent to the current round number
home.row5-2: Get free rewards from the Battle Pass. Purchase the Battle Pass to get even more rewards!
home.row5-3: A new Battle Pass will include new rewards each season, including new Gods, Arenas, Finishers and more!
home.row5-4: Arenas - Change the look of your battlefield
home.row5-5: Finishers - Change the damage projectile your God inflicts on your enemies
home.row5-6: Chests - Open chests to gain rewards, including literal hats for your god
home.row6-2: +1 God slot at the start of the game
home.row6-4: Access to PLUS exclusive Gods that rotate monthly
home.row7-2: Win games in order to gain ranks
home.row7-3: New Spells rotated in and out every season
home.row7-4: New Gods and cosmetics added every Battle Pass
home.row7-6: High ranked Leaderboard players will be given unique cosmetics at the end of each season
